name: Query to add a GS
func:
var tab = []


var gs = {}

 
 //From the GS

gs.name = msg.payload.Name
gs.latitude = msg.payload.Lat
gs.longitude = msg.payload.Lon
gs.altitude = msg.payload.Alt
gs.elevation = msg.payload.El
gs.freq = msg.payload.Freq
gs.location = "[" + msg.payload.Lat + "," + msg.payload.Lon + "]"

//Default
gs.status = 1
tab.push(gs)

msg.payload = tab
return msg;

name: msg2dash
func:
var tjd = (msg.payload[0][msg.payload[1]].mjday-33282)+msg.payload[0][msg.payload[1]].mjfrac/86400
var time = 86400*tjd-631152000

var myDate = new Date(time *1000);
date= (myDate.toGMTString());

msg.payload = date
msg.topic = "Date"
return msg

name: Result-setter
Result message setter
func:
var tab = []
var gs = {}

var n = msg.payload.length

 //From the GS
gs.ergolmass = parseFloat(msg.payload[n-12])
gs.alti = parseFloat(msg.payload[n-10])
gs.sma = parseFloat(msg.payload[n-9])
gs.ecc = parseFloat(msg.payload[n-8])
gs.inc = parseFloat(msg.payload[n-7]).toFixed(4)
gs.raan = (parseFloat(msg.payload[n-6])).toFixed(4)
gs.aop = parseFloat(msg.payload[n-5]).toFixed(4)
gs.meananom = (parseFloat(msg.payload[n-4])+0.0).toFixed(4)
gs.meanmove = parseFloat(msg.payload[n-3]).toFixed(14)
gs.period = parseFloat(msg.payload[n-2])


tab.push(gs)

msg.payload = tab
return msg;
